trans-unit.source: The <xref uid="langword_csharp_ControlChars" name="ControlChars" href=""></xref> module contains constants used as control characters.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_ControlChars" name="ControlChars" href=""> </xref>模組包含常數做為控制字元。

trans-unit.source: These constants can be used anywhere in your code.
trans-unit.target: 這些常數可以使用程式碼中的任何位置。

trans-unit.source: This module supports the Visual Basic language keywords and run-time library members that provide constant control characters for printing and displaying text.
trans-unit.target: 這個模組支援的 Visual Basic 語言關鍵字和常數的控制字元提供列印和顯示文字的執行階段程式庫成員。
